  "Description": {
    "English": "A processed metal alloy, created in a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Refiner</span> from the <span class=\"name name-stellar\">stellar metals</span>: <span class=\"name name-commodity\">Copper</span>, <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Cadmium</span>, <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Emeril</span> and <span class=\"name name-technology\">Indium</span>.<br><br>The <span class=\"name name-special\">rarer</span> the stellar metal, the more Chromatic Metal it will produce.<br><br>This valuable metal is used in the creation of many <span class=\"name name-technology\">advanced technologies</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种处理过的合金，在<span class=\"name name-technology\">精炼机</span>中使用<span class=\"name name-stellar\">星球金属</span>制作：<span class=\"name name-commodity\">铜</span>、<span class=\"name name-fuel\">镉</span>、<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">艾梅里尔</span>和<span class=\"name name-technology\">铟</span>。<br><br>恒星上的金属越<span class=\"name name-special\">稀有</span>，它产出的彩色金属就越多。<br><br>这珍贵的金属可用于创建许多<span class=\"name name-technology\">高级技术</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一種加工金屬合金，以<span class=\"name name-technology\">精製機</span>加工以下<span class=\"name name-stellar\">星體金屬</span>而成：<span class=\"name name-commodity\">銅</span>、<span class=\"name name-fuel\">鎘</span>、<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">砪</span>、<span class=\"name name-technology\">銦</span>。<br><br>星體金屬<span class=\"name name-special\">越稀有</span>，能生產的有色金屬也越多。<br><br>這種珍貴金屬能用來製作許多<span class=\"name name-technology\">先進科技</span>。"
  },
