    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-special\">有色金屬</span>是以<span class=\"name name-technology\">精製機</span>加工以下<span class=\"name name-stellar\">星體金屬</span>而成：<span class=\"name name-commodity\">銅</span>、<span class=\"name name-fuel\">鎘</span>、<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">砪</span>、<span class=\"name name-technology\">銦</span>。<br>星體金屬<span class=\"name name-special\">越罕見</span>，能生產的有色金屬也越多。使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析護目鏡</span>尋找星球上的星體金屬資源礦床。"
